  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I’ve heard rumors that you’ve become a proper tailor now… Naturally, I have to see for myself if they were true. You seem to have built up some skill and experience—care to prove it?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Confident, are you? Hmph. Very well. Go defeat #r#o22#s#k near #m10004000# and craft #ba #t1002084##k, then bring it back. I’ll be watching."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "So, you haven’t reached that level yet, have you? Hmph… perhaps this is the limit of a human after all."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Let’s see… this is exceptionally well made. I didn’t expect a human to reach this level of craftsmanship. Yes, this is more than sufficient to be called a true tailor. Your dedication to honing your skills is… admirable. Very well—this deserves a special reward."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This #t4130000# is a special item that can alter an equipment’s abilities when used during crafting. It’s extremely delicate, so the results may disappoint you at times—but if handled properly, it could produce something beyond your expectations."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you wish to test the limits of your tailoring skills, I recommend using it. Continue your training—and don’t grow complacent."
        }
      },
